headline: Eli Lilly (LLY) Valuation Check After Positive Phase 3 Retevmo Results And GLP 1 Growth Momentum
summary: Eli Lilly (LLY) is back in focus after reporting statistically significant Phase 3 results for Retevmo in early stage RET fusion positive lung cancer, adding another clinical milestone to an already closely watched story. See our latest analysis for Eli Lilly. Against a backdrop of strong GLP 1 obesity and diabetes demand, upbeat 2026 revenue guidance and ongoing buybacks, Eli Lilly’s 1 year total shareholder return of 24.1% and very large 5 year total shareholder return of about 4.4x suggest...
